channel.title: Webclients (im making them free along with showing you how to do so)
channel.description: I'm getting annoyed with these stupid "new" tutorials. each getting more and more dumb. Just send me your e-mail (hotmail only) or pm me. I will upload the webclient to a specific host for you or send the webclient to you through means of a filesharing site. I will do any version of any client as long as the ENTIRE source is open. Anything closed (say the signlink) will cause failure and i will be forced to decompile it myself.
